column2: The Bokor. You chose a difficult path. {nl}Refer to the instructions in Adventure Journal and make your own doll.
You can only get it by yourself. {nl}Check your Adventure Journal on how you can make the doll.
Congratulations, a new Bokor is born. {nl}When I first chose the path of Bokor, I started by creating a doll of my own.
Peltasta Master
How can you bear the name of Peltasta if you can't even handle that?
Good. {nl}I hope your new growth leads to you saving the world.
Highland Master
Hurry. {nl} It's a simple challenge, but Vubbes are a threat to the Miner's Village.
Good work, you've completed your initiation in becoming a Highlander. {Nl} Keep up the hard work and dedication.
Pyromancer Master
I can see that you want to learn magic from me but I can't teach just anyone. {nl}I will see how well you can assist my research and then decide.
Good work. Thanks to you I can go on to the next step for my research. {nl}I will teach you Pyromancer magic as promised.
Good, you're here. I need you to defeat the evil spirits I summon. {nl}I will record the unique wavelength that is transmitted in the process.
I am researching on the 4th state of matter. {nl}It is impossible without the cooperation of the Bokor Master who deals with the spirits.
Yes, that's great. {nl}Tell the Pyromancer Master that we have all the materials we need.
Good. {nl}That study is being done with the Bokor Master, so go to her and she'll tell you what to do.
Cryomancer Master
You want to learn Cryomancer magic from me? {nl}Sure I'll teach you. Only if you take care of something first.
The Pyromancer Master is not around. {nl}Well, it's an easy task.
Don't feel guilty about it. You did a good job. {nl}I've got your back from now on, so you don't need to worry.
It's sneaking into the Pyromancer Master's room and opening a box. {nl}And what's inside the box.. Well, you better just kill it off.
This will be enough. {nl}My magic is not easy so you need to work hard to keep up.
Your will to learn from me is good, but first I have a favor to ask. {nl}We can continue our talk if you say you're up to it. {nl}
Lydia Schaffen's stuff is like divine materials to us archers. {nl}I would give up everything just to have it.
I never imagined that I would see this myself. {nl}Thank you. I will teach you thoroughly from now on, so you better be prepared.
I heard the lost telescope lens from Star Tower is in the 1st floor of the Crystal Mines. {nl}Get me that lens before the other masters find out and I'll teach you my skills.
So you want to learn the way of the arrow from me.. Then I have a mission for you. {nl}I will base my decision on how well you accomplish the mission.
Evonipon.. I will never forgive that.
Hunter Master
You collected all the books. Good job. {nl}I will teach you the way of the hunters as promised.
You got some sure results. I will teach you from now on. {nl}I hope you live up to my expectations.
I heard the bats in Crystal Mines 1st Floor have special venom. {nl}I'm sure it's the venom used by the assassin Ebonipon. Bring me that venom.
Barbarian Master
You can understand an opponent's abilities by facing them sword on sword. {nl}Prove to me that you are a true warrior, and I will lead you in becoming a real Barbarian.
You indeed qualify as a warrior. {nl}I will make you become a true Barbarian.
I understand that you want to be stronger with a spear. {nl}Complete the mission I assign to you, and I will teach you my spearmanship.
I understand your will to become stronger. {nl}I think you have what it takes to be good with spears.
Psychokino Master
The Matsums attacked you? {nl}Since the Matsums accepted the Matsum dolls as their friends, I consider it successful.
Good work. {nl}You've done a good job as my assistant, so I'll teach you what being a Psychkino truly means.
My research is about the methods of shifting psychokinesis to the substance of matter. {nl}In other words.. It's a method of brainwashing by using medicine.
Linker Master
Talent is very important for Linkers. {nl}Closing one's heart is easy but opening others' requires special talents. {nl}
I will test you to see if you have such talent.
Great job. {nl}But this is only a preparation for the test. {nl}
It's just reality for normal people, but if you have the talent of a Linker, {nl}you will be able to find the hidden world. {nl}Find the book from there and bring it to me.
You brought the book. You have passed the test. {nl}Please read that book as your determination as a Linker.
Skills of a Sapper.. Then surely you must pay for it. {nl}Not to me. Instead, I want you to give a donation to the Cleric Master in Klaipeda. {nl}Around 5000 silvers?
Oh, this. I saw it somewhere.. hmm.. looks familiar.. {nl}Well I'll take it with thanks since you're giving it to me.
Huh, this is the tool I lost. {nl}Thank you. Where have it been.
Did you forget about the donation? {nl}It's 5000 silver.
Cleric Master
Thank you in the name of Goddess.{nl}I promise the donations will be used for those injured by monsters. {nl}
I used to be a thief, but I came to realize certain things and I stopped my life of crime. {nl}But there is a little load left on my mind.. and I will really end it this time {nl}
Anyway, you did a good job. {nl}Let's get along well from now on, teaching and learning from each other.
I'm looking for a book. Four books of Lydia Schaffen. {nl}If you help me find the books, I will teach you my skills.
The book used to be in Miner's town but it was lost when the Vubbes raided. {nl} Try going to the Vubbe Outpost.
It's this book. You will need this book if you dream to be the best Archer. {nl}I will make you a copy if you can gather all the books.
This is of good quality. The Hunter Master will be pleased. {nl}You can take the book. {nl}
The Archer Master in Klaipeda has the next book. {nl}He's not a mean person so he will give you the book if you ask nicely. {nl}
He is helping with the repair of the damaged city wall. {nl}I heard there are rocks moved to Miner's Village, so bringing him that rock can be a way to ask.
Did the Hunter Master send this rock? {nl}If it's Lydia Schaffen's book, you could have just asked. But thank you anyway.
The last book is with the Ranger Master in Klaipeda. {nl}Give her this pouch. {nl}I could go myself but we're not really comfortable seeing each other.
Don't ask why. Work is work, and it's a fact that we don't want to face each other.
This pouch.. Did you come for the Hunter Master? {nl}Here. Give her this book.
I don't want to act mean when she's acting humble.
This leather will be enough. {nl}Go to the Quarrel Shooter Master before someone else takes it.
This rock will be useful in repairing the wall. {nl}Bring it to the Archer Master quickly.
Are you the one who wants to learn my skills? {nl}Great, I was just looking for someone to help me find Lydia Shaffen's book. {nl}You're going to help right?
There is one in Miner's Village but it was lost when the Vubbes raided. {nl} I'm sure it's in the Vubbe Outpost.
Oh yes, this is it. {nl}This will be helpful for people like you, who dream of becoming a Quarrel Shooter. {nl}I will give you a copy if you collect all the books.
Three more left. {nl}I think you can get one of it by handing some money to the Hunter Master..
The problem is, I'm broke.
You mean Lydia Schaffen's book that I have? {nl}I'll hand it over for 5000 silvers.
Well then, thanks for your help. {nl}Around 5000 silver will do. {nl}
5000 silver.. Yup, that's right. {nl}I'll give you the book as promised.
Well.. the Archer Master must have the next book. {nl}He's still helping repair the wall so wouldn't he like it if you got him some stones? {nl}I could take it to him myself but.. owwww.. my back..
The Archer Master has the next book. {nl}He's not a mean person so he will give you the book if you ask nicely. {nl}
I heard he is helping repair the damaged city wall. {nl}There are rocks moved to Miner's Village so he'll be moved if you bring him that rock.
Did the Hunter Master send this rock? {nl}If it's Lydia Schaffen's book, you could have just asked. But thank you anyway.
Now, for the last book. {nl}Give this pouch to the Ranger Master and get the book.
Did the Quarrel Shooter send this? {nl}Thanks. I'll hand over the book as promised.
Bring the book quickly. {nl}I can't hold it.
Great, it's this one! {nl}I'll teach you the skills of Quarrel Shooter as promised. {nl}
This rock will be useful in repairing the wall. {nl}Bring it to the Archer Master quickly.
If you want to learn more of my skills, there is a condition. {nl}I want you to help me find the four books of Lydia Schaffen.
I heard the first book was with a resident in Miner's Village before the Vubbes attacked. {nl}So I think it could be in the Vubbe Outpost.
I'm surprised you found it so fast! {nl}And it's in a good state. {nl}
I think you might be able to buy the next book from the Hunter Master..{nl}I'm broke after fixing the wall with my money. Haha..
You mean the second book of Lydia Schaffen? {nl}I'll hand it over for 5000 silver.
I think around 5000 silver will do. {nl}I heard that's the book's value.
The quality is fine enough. The Archer Master must also be pleased. {nl}Here, I've prepared a copy, so take it.
Now there is one book left. {nl}Give this pouch to the Ranger Master and get the book. {nl}
Did the Archer Master send you? {nl}Well, good work. I'll give you the book as promised.
Isn't the book ready yet? {nl}I want to see all of Lydia Schaffen's book ASAP..
Finally it's all here. {nl}I'll teach you my skills as promised.
I have some books to collect. It's Lydia Schaffen's books. {nl}I'll teach you my skills if you collect the books. What do you say?
The first book was in the Miner's Village but it was gone after the Vubbes attacked. {nl}I assume the book is in the Vubbe Outpost?
Oh, that's pretty good. {nl}It will he helpful for you to read it too.
The problem is the Hunter Master. I really don't want to see her face. {nl}So you go and get the next book from her.
You mean the book I have? {nl}Well, okay. I'll hand it over for 5000 silver.
I think around 5000 silver will do. {nl}Can you spare that much?
The book is in good condition.{nl}Now, bring the book to the Archer Master. {nl}
The Archer Master in Klaipeda has the last book. {nl}I heard he is repairing the wall so this might help you get the book?
I heard there is a rock useful for repairing the wall in Miner's Village. {nl}Bring that to the Archer Master as a present.
Did the Ranger Master send this rock? {nl}If it's Lydia Schaffen's book, you could have just asked. Anyway, thank you.
You finally collected them all. Good work. {nl}I will teach you my skills as promised but it's your job to keep track and follow.
You got some pretty good leather. {nl}Bring it to the Quarrel Shooter Master.
Why did you bring that to me? Take it to the Archer Master quickly.
Sculptor Tesla
A sculptor's talent is important but so is having the eye to see important materials. {nl}I will help you learn my skills if you bring me the blue crystals I'm looking for.
That is the problem. {nl}The Yekub swallowed it as soon as it was found on the 2nd Floor of the Miner's Village.
Oh, this is it. {nl}I have a lot of time so I will teach you slowly.
You want to learn the swordsmanship of a Highlander from me? {nl}I will consider it if you can get cooperation from the Peltastas.
Thank you for the supplies, but the Highlander Master wouldn't have sent you for nothing. {nl}Tell me what you want. {nl}
An overall cooperation between the Masters. Alright. {nl}Tell him that the Peltastas are for it.
If the Masters unite, it won't be long until the kingdom rises again. {nl}You did a good job. I will teach you my swordsmanship.
That is enough. {nl}Get the Peltasta's cooperation with it.
We, Peltastas, consider our duties as humans to be most important.
I was about to ask for aid in the search. {nl}
These.. were their keepstakes. {nl}We can at least give the keepstakes to their families. Thank you. {nl}
I will tell the Highlander Master myself, so please go back. {nl}Good work.
It might not be a pleasant feeling, but that's good enough. {nl}I will allow you to learn the way of the Peltasta as promised.
I need to gather the energy of fire for my research, but I just don't have time. {nl}If you gather it for me, I will help you learn the magic of Pyromancers.
Be careful. The port will break if you don't keep an eye on it.
There is an important book that I'm looking for. {nl}If you get me that book, I will help you learn the magic of Cryomancers.
Did you say you'll find the book? {nl}Sorry but you're late.
I heard rumors that it's in Miner's Village but I don't know the exact source of it. {nl}Maybe the Mayor would know..
The Vubbes took all the books when they attacked. {nl}Maybe they will use it for fire in their outpost.
If there was something like that, we would have taken care of it. {nl}You go and try looking for it.
You found it. Great job. {nl}You'll have to work real hard to follow my trainings.
I heard the book was last seen in Miner's Village. {nl}It's a very important book so maybe the Mayor might know.
You must have found the book. I don't know how, but congratulations. {nl}Why don't you go back to the one who's waiting for that book?
Krivis Master
Krivis should be free from the constraints of humans and dedicate themselves to the clergy. {nl}This is done by offering dedication prayers to all the Goddess Statues in Siauliai. {nl}
Repent. {nl}Ask the Goddess for forgiveness and be born brand new.
I can feel that you are full of the Goddess' blessings. {nl}Welcome to your new world as Krivis.
Swordsman Master
An old saying goes, fight to death and you will survive. {nl}I will be able to teach you if you come to realize what it means.
You haven't realized what it means. {nl}Fight a bit more.
Right.. Now do you understand. {nl}Remember that you're a Swordsman and devote yourself to being one.
The most important thing for Priests is to belief in the Goddess, and to prove it. {nl}Exorcise the soldiers possessed with evil spirits in the name of Goddess.
That soldier is being taken care of in Miner's Village. {nl}Your sincerity will become your strength.
Your sincerity has been proven. {nl}We will walk together in the name of the Goddess.
Learning magic from me comes after helping my research. {nl}Let's talk about the talent problem afterwards.
You've gathered everything. {nl}Now let's move on to the next step.
Klaipeda is far from the capital and was barely attacked by the monsters. {nl}I paid attention to that point and I am studying to make a great magic circle. {nl}
And for that, I need to accumulate data. {nl}Can you use this scroll around the city?
I've marked on the map where you need to install it. {nl}You need to use it on every single point.
Good work. I've gathered some useful data with your help. {nl}My research is complete so you can come to train anytime.
You must have come to learn the faith of Clerics. {nl}I will teach you if you help by treating the injured soldiers of Miner's Village.
The Cleric Master shines light to many at such a young age. {nl}Take this holy water and go to the patients quickly.
You need the holy water to treat them. {nl}You should get the holy water from the Priest Master and the Krivis Master first.
If it's for the Cleric Master, take as much holy water as you need. {nl}She has a beautiful heart that even this old priest would envy.
Please send my regards to the Cleric Master. {nl}May the blessings of Goddess be with you.
Please send them my regards while you get holy water from the masters.
Service is what you do for others, but it is also a way of cleansing your own reflection. {nl}I hope your wandering soul will be cleansed as you treat the patients.
Good job. {nl}I will teach you the faith of Clerics as promised.
I think that you may not have a great spear right away {nl}but you must have a spear that you are strongly attached to. {nl}How do you think about it?
Spears are the pride of Hoplites. {nl}A strong spear is something that Hoplites can boast like their name.
That's great. {nl}Alright. You have what it takes to learn spearmanship from me.
Alright. {nl}If you want my recognition, show me a spear upgraded to level 6.{nl}
You want to learn Quarrel Shooter Skills from me? {nl}Right on time. I was also looking for someone to help me.
You were sent by the Quarrel Shooter Master, right? {nl}You must find the map. A map hidden with Fletcher's secrets.
The Sapper Master says he found some information about the book I'm looking for. {nl}Go to Siauliai Eastern Woods and meet him.
Oh, is this the map? Good job. {nl}I'll teach you my skills as promised.
Is this the map? I really can't tell. {nl}Take it to the Quarrel Shooter Master.
So you came to learn more skills from me. {nl}Then go help the Rodelero Masters in Fedimian. I will evaluate you based on that.
Did the Archer Master send you?{nl}Klaipeda is becoming stable but Fedimian is still at risk.
I hear that most of Fedimian, aside from Divine Area, is buried and in need of help.
I want you to defeat the boss monster in Mage Tower. {nl}Monsters are pouring out of the tower {nl}and we are having troubles as it is rebuilding Fedimian.
According to the scout who made it in, there was a Minotaur on the 3rd Floor of the Mage Tower. {nl}Defeating it will be good enough to serve as a warning.
Well done. Thanks to you, the monsters have been warded off. {nl}Extend my gratitude to the Archer Master as well.
Well done. {nl}I will train you to be stronger as promised.
You want to learn the skill of Ranger from me? {nl}Okay. If you help me, I'll consider it depending on how you do.
I heard you're looking for someone who wears a hoodie and has a unique scent. {nl}
Of course I remember. It was a man with a dangerous scent. {nl}He asked about materials that not many people know about so I thought he was strange. {nl}
Evoniphon.. I will never forget it.
How would I know his whereabouts. {nl}He asked about materials I did not have so I told him where he could get it.
This scent.. yes, it's Evoniphon's.{nl}This will be enough. I will teach you my skills as promised.
Yes, this is the scent. {nl}It was very unique so I couldn't forget it even if I wanted to. {nl}
Hey, if you came here to be stronger, you've come to the right place. {nl}But you can't have it for nothing. You have to do me a favor. {nl}
Oh, right. You should be able to do it easily if you want to become a Sapper. {nl}Now you just have to help with the experiment.
Well, it's pretty simple. {nl}Check how effective this bomb is on the monsters in Siauliai Eastern Woods.
I hope it works this time..
They fell back without much damage? {nl}Hmm, what could the problem be.. I need to check from the beginning again. {nl}
Anyways, Thanks. {nl}You can come back anytime if you want to learn my skills.
You want to learn about the Bokors? {nl}Then first, get me a card that you can get from powerful monsters.
It doesn't matter which card it is as long as it's from the powerful monster. {nl}What you will bring to me is already decided.
Complete. Traveler. Promised victory. Perfected world. {nl}Finding a full interpretation is up to you.
Sometimes the destined, harsh fate can lead to the dark future. {nl}I will lead you through the path of the Bokor as promised.
I'm looking for a cat that can model but I'm old and it's not easy. {nl}Bring a suitable cat and I'll teach you my skills.
Grandpa Tesla wants a cat? {nl}There are plenty of cats over at Klaipeda Plaza, but {n1}it won't be easy to catch one without special food.
I like cats because they do the basics. {nl}The cats have all lines.
I can give you the special food for catching a cat. {nl}If you find my father, I will give it to you for free!
I'll give you the special cat food as promised. {nl}It's made with stuff that the cats like so it should work.
Oh oh, it's that cat. {nl}I'll make you stronger as promised. {nl}
I've traded for a long time with a Klaipeda Item Merchant, so they might help you.
I want you to do something in return for learning magic from me. {nl}It's simple but a little dangerous. Would you like to give it a try? {nl}
If you find it dangerous, please leave immediately. {nl}I'll just have to find another disciple.
Good work. {nl}I will teach you the magic of Pyromancer as promised. {nl}
I can promise you a higher level of strength. {nl}Of course, it won't come for free.
Well done. {nl}I will help you become stronger.
You've come to the right palce if you want to practice stronger magic. {nl}But you can't learn from me with your weak determination.
I can see you passion but what about your abilities? {nl}Bring the piece of Phyracon and scale of Green Drake from Maze Tower.
Great job. But I am a bit fussy. {nl}I will decide depending on how well you assist my work.
I used to research on town defense magic and I think we can try that in Fedimian. {nl}But in roder to do that, I neet a lot of data. {nl}
Your job is to use this data recording scrolling in Fedimian,
I've marked on the map where you should use it. {nl}Use it each location.
Good work. You wanted to take magic to the next level right? {nl}I'm very stricct so I hope you follow along well.
Healing the body also heals the soul. {nl}If you want to take yourself to the next level, then service to others by healing them.
There are still many people who need the help of treatment. {nl}Share your kindness with them.
Goddess helps those who help. {nl}It may not be much, but I hope I can be of help in taking you to the next level.
The Cataphract.. {nl}I'm not sure if you have the strength to learn it.
Great work. You seem good enough to learn my skills. {nl}Ah. I apologize for underestimating you.
It's putting all your focus on one point and skweing the enemy. {nl}Of course, you are not yet at that level so I'll approve if you just defeat it.
Sorcerer Master
If you want to learn magic from me, you should show me how good you are. {nl}It's simple. Win a magic duel against me.
Don't be scared. I'll take it down to your level. {nl}I'll meet you in the vacant area of the plaza.
Alright. You seem good enough. {nl}You can come to me anytime you want to learn magic.
Necromancer Master
Necromancer's spells eat up the spell caster if the soul is not trained enough. {nl}Fight me and prove how strong your soul is.
Wait in the vacant area of the plaza
Well, that will be good enough for a start. {nl}I'll pass you the spell of Necromancers.
Druid Master
You need to awaken your senses first if you want to become a Druid. {nl}I'll awake your sense to commune with nature through a duel.
There's not enough space here so I'll see you at the plaza'a vacan't area.
You have some special senses. {nl}If I can lead you well as a Druid, your future will look promising.
Only combat makes us stronger. {nl}Prove yourself if you want to learn from me!
Our ways are simple. {nl}If you leave, you have what it takes and if not, you don't. {nl}Since you are alive, you are worth it.
If you are qualified, I will take your mana to the next level as a Linker. {nl}It doesn't matter which magic it is. I'll test you through a duel.
I tested you at your level and you are good enoug. {nl}I will help you sharpen your mana as promised.
Hunters talk only with arrows. {nl}I will have it down to your level so if you want to learn from me, {nl}you have to overcome me.
You won this duel. {nl}I will train you as promised.
You must have the strength if you want to learn the Highlander's sword. {nl}Show me what you have. {nl}{nl}
I see that you have bravery and strength that suits it. {nl}I will take you to the next level with the honor of Highlander.
I understand your bravery with this. {nl}Always make yourself a proud one for your shield.
Sincerety is the strength of Krivis. {nl}Prove your sincerity through duel.
The duel will take place in Highlander Master's Training Room. {nl}I will see you there.
Your sincerity as firm as the stone pillars. {nl}I'll lead you to a higher level as promised.
The faith of Priests should be unshakable no matter what. {nl}I will test to see how strong your faith is through a duel. {nl}
The duel will take place in Highlander Master's Training Room. {nl}You go first.
I see that your faith is strong from the outside but deep inside, I see hesitation. {nl}
Throw away the hesitation and fill it with the garce of Goddess. {nl}I will help you reach a higher level through the grace.
The sword we, Swordsmans, swing should have no hesitation. {nl}Hesitation is a gap in the heart. The enemy always looks out for that gap. {nl}
Minotaurs is in Maze Tower 3rd Floor. {nl}Fight it and throw away any hesitation of the sword.
Hesitation is a dangerous weakness. {nl}I hope you can realize that.
Alright.. You have what it takes to further develop yourself. {nl}Keep devoting yourself to training.
Centrurion Master
The Centurion. It's not an easy path. {nl}But it's a different story if you win a duel with me. What do you think?
The duel will take place in plaza vacant lot so be there first.
That is enough. {nl}I will be responsible for teaching you.
Sadhu's training being from training your soul to become stronger. {nl}I will check though a duel.. to see if your soul is prepared enough to take our trainings.
I can see your will. {nl}Welcome to joining the Sadhu.
Hackapell Master
It's good that you want to learn my combat skills but first, I need to check your abilities. {nl}I need to know your weakness in order to teach you, isn't it?
I'll see you in the plaza vacant area. {nl}Be there first.
This seems enough. {nl}Harsh trainings wil begin from now.
Wugushi Master
Wugushi s don't hesitate on using poison. {nl}Before you learn anything, I'll show you how we fight. {nl}Arrows or airguns, I'll show you with whatever it takes.
Saw it? This is how Wugushis fight. {nl}You need to throw your guilt about using foul methods if you want to be a Wugushi.
If you really want to be a Rodelero, checking your shield again. {nl}When I first chose the path of Rodelero, I began with getting a level 6 shield.
Prepare a level 6 shield. {nl}I need to check your will at least.
You have perseverance unlike the rest of the youth nowadays. {nl}Come by anytime if you want to learn.
I trust my judgement more than anybody. {nl}I will check througha duel if you have what it takes to be with the Squires.
The sword will be sharper when you believe in yourself.
I can see your skills. {nl}I hope you will be even greater from now on with my teachings.
Thaumaturge Master
Thaumaturge magic is one of the most difficult magics but I can lead you well. {nl}Do me a favor and I will guide your path of Thaumaturge.
Put aside the boring theories and get to the actual battle. {nl}It's a simple mission. Go back if you don't wish to fulfill it.
Good work. {nl}Since you've done your mission, let's begin the duel right away.
Scout Master
Scout doesn't mean you're only good at hiding and infiltraion. {nl}You also need to have combat skills if you're a true scout. {nl}
Prove yourself in a duel with me, then I'll teach you my secret skills.
You have pretty good senses. {nl}But my trainings can't be done by sense alone so better keep up.
Paladin Master
We have followed the Goddess and fought for justice and belief.{nl}If you truly want to learn from the Paladins, you need to prove your faith.
At least you weren't a bluffer. {nl}Good. I will approve your learning from Paladin.
So you want to learn from the Highlanders. {nl}Alright. But there is a condition.
You're the support from Highlander Master. {nl}It's urgent so I'll get to the point right away.
There's a problem in Crystal Mines and Commander Uska asked us for support. {nl}But we, the Peltastas, also don't have time right now.{nl}
So I want you to help Commander Uska for us.
Pledge is important. {nl}I cannot accept anything taht breaks the trust int he confusing current state.
I thought it would be difficult even as we asked for support. {nl}But now we're relieve that you're the support.
Highlander and Peltasta's Honor is on the line. {nl}Please help commander Uska well.
There are rumors that a huge monster is roaming Crystal Mines 2nd Floor. {nl}But the mines is an important industry for Klaipeda so we can't just stay doing nothing. {nl}
So please check Crystal Mines 2nd Floor and get rid of the source of rumors.
Safety of the villagers is on the line. {nl}Please check it well.
I can't believe there is still that kind of thing left.. {nl}It's a relief that no one was hurt. {nl}We should consider sending the elite troops until the Mines is stable.
Anyway, thanks for the hard work and send my thanks to Highlander Masetr. {nl}I will thank Peltasta Master when I meet him soon.
Good work. Now the Pelatastas owe me another one.{nl}I will lead you as Highlander Master as promised.
Seems like I get your help a lot. {nl}Please take care of Klaipeda in the future too.
You want to learn from me? {nl}Alright, I'll accept the offer if you do me a favor.
Did Peltasta Master send you? {nl}If it's about the shield, I already know it.
If we don't get the supplies, then we don't have to keep the pledge with Highlanders. {nl}Also, our trust will be broken.
I should have sent a letter of apology but I wasn't able to. {nl}There will be word from a client soon so wait for a while.
Fletcher Master
Did you come from Klaipeda? {nl}You can't even if you rush it. Go back.
Did you not hear me? {nl}Your turn is far behind.
I've never been this mad since that tree took my workshop to the sky {nl}4 years ago on Divine Day.
Did you get rid of it? That's great to hear. {nl}One less reason for the lazy Fedimian merchants.
I will be able to send the rest of the stuff soon as promised. {nl}You can go back now. I need to concentrate.
I can keep a good relationship with Highlander with your help. {nl}I will lead you as Peltasta Master as promised.
I will send my disciple to Highlander Master so don't worry about that.
It's emotional to see that there's someone willing to learn from a person like me. {nl}Alright, if you get me back my things, I will teach you the skills of Corsair.
Now that's something! {nl}I will teach you the skill of Corsair as promised.
Fight with all you've got. I will show you how to fight with sword and shield. {nl}Remember that it depends on your abilities that I could teach you or desert you.
Are you thinking otherwise even when your best is not enough?
You have a bad habit. But it could be changed. {nl}I teach strictly so better be prepared.
Teaching you skills is not difficult as long as you do me a favor. {nl}
There's something I requested to Fletcher Master but there's no news yet. {nl}I want you to check it. I'm more worried about the person than the thing..
Did Archer Master worry? I'm fine. {nl}If there's a problem, it's that the materials can't follow my crafting speed.
Well he's hot tempered much so.. Please take care of it.
I think it'll be over soon if you gather good stones from Penitence Route of Cathedral. {nl}Around 150 of it will do. I'll give you a bag for it.
I wish there was a well flowing with the materials. {nl}It's my lifelong wish.
The Golems? That's strange. {nl}Maybe the Goddess helped.{nl}
Done. Take it. {nl}Send my regards to Archer Master.
I was just going to send you an errand. Sorry for the Golems. {nl}Anyway, I'll pass you my skills as promised.
I have no business with you. {nl}I'm busy. Go back.
You came to me to learn the skill of ranger right? {nl}I'll give it a positive consideration if you do me a favor.
I can't get a grasp of what the eboniphons are doing.{nl}I'm sure it's not something good but I can't even tell its objectives and it's making me mad.
So these must be the samples. This will be good enough for our trade. {nl}Alright, I'll make you become stronger.
You want to learn my skills? {nl}I'll think about it if you get me the tree I'm looking for.
Ah, that' right. Just throw it there somewhere. {nl}It's nothing hard so i'll teach you, but if it disturbs my work, {nl}then it'll stop right away.
Since you've done the mission well, I'll teach you about the Hunter's way. {nl}Good work.
It's ahrd to stray away from the charm of poison. I'm one of them. {nl}I'll let you know how appealing it is too. Let's start slowly from today.
No one can hide perfectly from the scouts.
You did it easier than I thought.{nl}Great. I think it'll be fun to teach you. {nl}Come to me anytime you want to learn from me.
I think you're good enough to be accepted as my disciple but you still need to be tested. {nl}I will welcome you if you bring the rubbings fo Lydis Schaffen's gravestone in the courtyard of Goddess.
It's the gravestone of the person all archers look up to. {nl}Do it well so that all the writings are readable.
I used to be a Schaffenstar back in the day.{nl}Anyway, I will teach you my skills as promised.
Rogue Master
Preternatural swiftness is the flower of the Rogues. {nl}It's getting your mind confused with the swift movement.
I thought it would be difficult but you're great at it. {nl}I will teach you the skills slowly so better warm up first.
You need to show your bravery if you want to learn from me. {nl}Use this note to provoke the monsters in Penitence Route. {nl}
Are you brave enough to turn the enemy's blade to you when your allies are in danger?
I can picture them full of anger. {nl}You've passed the test. You're good enough to learn from me.
The spear is unbeatable and invincible. {nl}I want to see the face of poor Shadow Gaoler when it's defeated.
You want to learn from me? {nl}Then you have to pass a test. {nl}
If you have the abilities to learn from me, then Yekub will be easy enough.
I want to see their faces who would fight Yekub that doesn't even exist. {nl}Alright, you're good enough.
Welcome to becoming a Centurion. {nl}You'll learn step by step about the formation from now.

Squires are strong but we shine more when helping our partners. {nl}Using the rope to make connecting attacks with fellow colleagues {nl}is an attack that is especially stonger than any other attacks.
Nobody should make any mistakes for connecting attacks to succeed. {nl}That is why you need to practice hard.
How much are you used to it? {nl}I will teach you thoroughly as promised.
Going through these dangers can be a good experience.
The Peltastas requested for help. {nl}We are tight with our troops but we also can't reject the Peltastas as we have a pledge with them.
I want you to assist the Peltastas and carry out the mission.
We, Peltatas, receive shield supplies as a condition for keeping our pledge with Highlanders. {nl}The shield always have been supplied on time but recently, the supplies have been cut. {nl}
Ask the Highlander what the problem is and if you can, please solve it.
I'm following the traces of Eboniphons.{nl}Recent information says that they tested something in the Cathedral.{nl}
You go to the Cathedral right away and get a sample of Moya's fluid. {nl}We'll be able to know something if we examine that.
I'll give you this flare since you're a novice. {nl}It will help you find the monsters easily.
Poison is like a blade with two sides so you should be careful with it. {nl}Especially if you get a finger cut while using the poison..
I assume you've come to learn something from me because you have the abilities. {nl}Something like winning a duel with me.
Go to the vacant area above the stairs and wait. {nl}I'll be there after finishing this up.
You're faster than you seem. {nl}I will teach you my skills from now on so come anytime.
I heard the Minotaurs showed up. {nl}If you want to learn from me, you should be able to hunt it down easily.
If you didn't go, I would have gone myself. {nl}I'm yielding it for you so better be thankful about it.
Great. You have my recognition. {nl}Come by anytime if you want to learn the skills of Hunters.
I'm relieved you're here. {nl}Everyone is focused there but only us, Rangers, are not dispatched.
I heard you were a step faster than Hunters. {nl}Good work. I'm very strict with teaching so better be prepared.
Teaching the skills of Scouts is not difficult. {nl}But you need to have the capacity to follow it, isn't it?
Good job. You did it faster than I expected. {nl}Come by anytime if you want to learn something.
You want to learn Sapper skills from me? That's a good idea. {nl}I am lacking materials for developing a new trap.{nl}
So you will need to help me with it. {nl}Can you defeat Rocktortuga in Ruklys Memorial and bring me Natural Mano Stones?
It's Rocktortuga of Ruklys Memorial. {nl}Rocktortugas in other areas don't give Mano Stones.
Alright. Got the Mano Stones..{nl}Come by anytime if you want to learn Sapper skills.
In other words, it's impossible.
You have unreasonably great skills. {nl}I'd welcome a disciple like you. I will teach you the skills.
Would it make sense if Wugushi is poisoned and weak?
Our teachings are harsh so I hope you understand. {nl}Anyway, you can come anytime if you want to learn.
I'm so ashamed of my disciples ruining all the commissions. {nl}If you do a good job, I will teach you Quarrel Shooter skills.
It's the Temple Shooter in Town Central. {nl}My disciples even ran away when it was right in front so prepare yourself for it.
You defeated it. Now I feel better. {nl}Come for lessons anytime. I'll teach you wholeheartedly.
Schwarze Reiter
I need to test if you are qualified to learn my skills. {nl}Sparnas Horn seems right enough for someone like you, what do you think?
I heard Sparnas Horn is huge so it spends most of its time on the ground than on air.
I didn't expect you to defeat it. That's pretty good. {nl}Alright. You can come anytime you want to learn skills.
You want to reach a higher level through the calling of Clerics. {nl}I will help you achieve it through service.
There are many people waiting for treatment but there is not enough medicinal herbs. {nl}Please get Nicotia herbs from the Centurion Master in Pilgrim's Way.{nl}
It's be a long journey. {nl}May the blessings of Goddess be with you always.
Ah, the Cleric Master sent you. {nl}Nice to meet you. I'm Centurion Master.
Unfortunately, we're out of Nicotia that the Cleric Master is asking for. {nl}There was an urgent request so it had to be used.
But don't worry. {nl}Nicotias grow all over the place so it'll be fine if you just take the young shoots.
Nicotia is not far away from here. {nl}Send my regards to the Cleric Master.
Thank you. This will help many people in pain. {nl}The Goddess will also be glad for your reaching higher level of Clerics.
If you want to step up as Krivis, then go and worship the Goddess Statue in Fedimina. {nl}Pilgrimage is a sure way to fulfill duties to the Goddess.
Take offering before you leave. {nl}The Priest Master and Cleric Master will give you the offering needed for worship.
You're leaving for the pilgrimage. {nl}I can still remember my journey to pilgrimage when I was a young clergy.
You can feel your heart filling with faith when you look at the Goddess Statue in Fedimian.
I can give you the offering materials.{nl}But before that, I have a favor to ask you. {nl}
Residents are complaining about the Rock Tortuga running wild in Siauliai Western Woods. {nl}I will give you the offerings if you get rid of that monster.
The Goddess will also be happy for your mercy.{nl}Here, take the offerings. {nl}
The Goddess will also be happy for your mercy.{nl}I also want to visit Fedimian again if I could.
You're going on pilgrimage to Fedimian.{nl}Here, take the offerings.
The Goddess Statue is at the center of Fedimian. {nl}It's huge and wide so be careful not to get lost.
There's an interesting legend about the Goddess Statue in Fedimian. {nl}If you have the opportunity, it'll be good to find it too.
I can feel that you are full of the Goddess's blessings. {nl}Good work. Those blessings will lead you to a higher place.
Are you coming from Fedimian? {nl}Krivis Master is waiting for you.
Will you take on the vocation of Priest and follow the path of Goddess? {nl}You can do so by getting rid of evil.
Evil forces are showing up in the Way of Big Starving Demon in Fedimian. {nl}Extract its identity from it and smudge it with the name of Goddess.
Anyone who follows the words of the Goddess can receive her powers to drive out evil spirits. {nl} But its strength will depend on the depth of faith.
Well done. {nl}In the name of the goddess, please judge those negative things so they can't put their feet on the ground.
If you want to research about the way of Bokor, you should do something for me.{nl}Please get the jewel from Krivi Master.
Bokor Master sent you?{nl}So they have decided to dispose that jewel.
It will be very dangerous.{nl}You should get prepared.
Take it. It is the jewel that is cursed by a vicious being.{nl}Several priests are trying to handle it, but they are having hard time.
Since we are also curious about that, please come back sometime later.
I feel something bad.{nl}I hope nothing bad occurs..{nl}
You've brought it.{nl}But.. damn..
The curse in this jewel is calling Tutu here.{nl}While I am handling this curse somehow, there is something that you should do.
First, tell Krivi Master to prepare the memorial service.{nl}After that, please go to the east forest of Siaulai and block Tutu.
This thing could happen when the power of the curse gets stronger.{nl}Our mission is to stop that.
Yes. In fact, that jewel is the one which an young priest from the village picked up.{nl}After he brought this jewel, he suffered from nightmares so I requested to Bokor Master.
Okay anyways. I will prepare the memorial service.{nl}Don't worry about it and you just block Tutu from the east forest of Siaulai before it comes to Klaipeda.
This thing happens since the world is in chaos.{nl}The goddess must feel sad about it..
I was able to deal with it cleverly because of your help.{nl}As a Bokor, I can expect your growth from now on.
You defeated that Tutu. Well done.{nl}As a result, I can prepare the memorial service without any problem.{nl}
Return to Bokor fast and tell him about it.

It's good that you learn the skills from me, but I want you to also understand the importance of the care after that.{nl}The priests at Klaipeda requsted to care for the statue of the goddess, how about it?
I want you to get the perfumed oil for the maintenance of the statue first.{nl}If you ask the priests, they will give it to you.
This is the perfumed oil.{nl}Since Tesla is too old, I was worried that my request may be too much, but i guess it's alright now.{nl}
This is all I have..{nl}I heard Krivi Master also has some.
Perfumed Oil? Ah, here it is.{nl}Please take care for the statue.
Please tell Tesla that I am okay.
Go meet Priest Master too.{nl}The amount of perfumed oil you have may not be enough.
That's the task we requested to you so if you need it, we will give to you. {nl}Here you go.
Even if you receive perfumed oil from Priest Master, it may not be enough.{nl}Since you should take care for it with the greatest care.
The amount of perfumed oil you have seems lacking a bit.{nl}Since Bokor Master also has the oil, why don't you go meet him?
Perfumed Oil? we will definitely give it to you.{nl}Tesla told us that he doesn't need any pay for that so we felt sorry about it.
Too bad I can't go with you since I don't have enough time.
The statues that we requested to you are the statue in Fedimian and the statue in Klaipeda.{nl}Okay then, I am counting on you.
If you use the absolute power of the goddess, you may get to Fedimian little easier.
Well don.{nl}Go back to Tesla.
It is also a task of Divdirbys to take care for the work besides creating the work.{nl}Don't forget about thie feeling if you want to learn the skills of Divdirbys.
Doing penance is not just for yourself, but to also be kind to others.
As you become kind to others, you will reach to a higher stage.{nl}As a Sadhu Master, I will lead that way for you.
First of all, Paladin shows by acting rather than telling.{nl}Prove your religious belief of the goddess by dueling against me.
First of all, the religious belief is the power to us, Paladins.{nl}You possess the great religious belief.{nl}
You passed the test.{nl}You should be prepared since I will train your spirit more harder from now on.
Monk Master
The religious belief gets completed when you have a well trained body.{nl}I will test you.
Good. Your religious belief is very strong.{nl}I will accept you as a monk. You should be prepared since our training is very hard.
Pardoner Master
Ordinally, the best way to get accepted as a Pardoner is to contribute a lot of money.{nl}But, I think completing an assignment would be better for you.{nl}
Please bring me the fire pot.{nl}I heard the rumor that the merchants in Fedimian saw that pot.
Wow! Welcome.{nl}Do you need anything?
Oh the Pardoner Master. {nl}There's a lot he doesn't know..
Oh. Yes! This is it.{nl}I will accept you as a Pardoner.
Please return to Pardoner Master.{nl}He was looking for the fire pot for a long time.
Fire Pot? Of course I know it.{nl}But you know I am a merchant. If you could get me the hardened oil from the monsters at Way of Big Starving Demon..
If you don't need it, then I am also good with it.{nl}Since I am busy, I will just do my work.
Oh, Thank you.{nl}A monster called Mostem keeps his hands on the fire pot all the time.{nl}
Ask the equipment merchant over there since he said he saw it recently.
Wizard is the magician who focus on the basics of all magics.{nl}If you seek a stronger magic, you should go back to the basics.{nl}
Please defeat the violent golem at the west forest of Siaulai.{nl}I will decide whether I will continue to teach you based on the result of it.
Huhu.{nl}I remember when you were a probationary wizard.
Yes. Well done.{nl}Let's start from the basics. I will help you with my best.
The Poatas are threatening the villagers at the east forest of Siaulai.{nl}If you could defeat that monster in the name of Gabiya goddess, I will teach you my magics.{nl}{nl}
One can say that he is strong when he shares it with others after learning something.
Well done. The goddess, Gabiya must be very satisfied.{nl}As promised, I will take you to the next stage of Pyromancer.
With the power of chilly air, you dream to reach to a higher stage.{nl}Mushcaria at the west forest of Siaulai will be a good assignment for you.
It's not good to see an weak human is chasing after strongness.
You did well without any shortages.{nl}As promised, I will train you harder.
Psychochino shows his power by believing his own abilities.{nl}You gotta show how much you trust yourself to receive my lessons.
The Red Bubbe Warriors in this forest are hard to fight against.{nl}But, if you trust yourself, you will be able to defeat it.
How are you going to use the super natural power if you don't trust yourself?{nl}Don't you think so?
Your abilities are way better than I expected.{nl}But, if you learn from me, you can reach to a higher stage.
Before you learn magics from me, I want to see how you control mana.{nl}Defeat the Bubbe Warrior at the west forest of Siaulai using any magic you want.
As you know more about Linker, it is very interesting.{nl}Don't you think so? Reading the string of mana..
You possess great abilities indeed.{nl}As a linker, if I could lead you well, you will become a really powerful magician.
Before you learn the magics of Thaumaturge, I need to test your magical skills.{nl}Defeat Burning Salamanders at Magicians' Tower.
It is important to measure your skills.{nl}It will be more important if you don't pass the test.
This is nice.{nl}I will help with my best efforts for your future development.{nl}{nl}
Very nice.{nl}You obtained the right to become more stronger with this.{nl}
You better give up if your will is not strong enough.{nl}If that's not it, Defeat Devil Gloves that are walking around here.
Evil spirits are just tools.{nl}I won't do anything that would turn my back on the goddess.
You really take every possible means.{nl}Well, we are the same about that. I will permit you learning magics from me.
Being a Necromancer is really nice.{nl}But, using humans as ingredients is forbidden.
Very nice indeed.{nl}You have no problem understanding my spells.
Chronomancer Master
No matter how strong a magic is, no magic can stop the time from flowing.{nl}But, it could be possible by Agailla Flurry..
You did way better than I expected.{nl}I will acknowledge your skills. Please follow me well from now on.
I don't know if those Masters really think about the safety of the goddess and the kingdom.{nl}Ironbaum is approaching Klaipeda, but no one is worried about it.
That attitude is what I wanted.{nl}I will teach you the true magic if you defeat Ironbaum at the west forest of Siaulai.
Especially the attitude of Creomancer really.. pisses me off.
I remember when you first arrived at Klaipedas.{nl}If you want, you can start the training right away.
Ironbaum is running around at the east forest of Siaulai rignt now.{nl}But, Chronomancer Master is not doing anything about it.{nl}
I know it is little ridiculous to ask a favor to a person who has come to learn my magic, but I have no other choice.{nl}I want you to defeat Ironbaum to teach him a lesson.
Klaipeda may fall into a danger, but he only cares about his safety. That's pathetic.
Well done.{nl}Creomancer Master woudn't stand and watch now since the Pyromancer trainee also stepped forward.{nl}Until then, let's talk about the fire magic slowly.
The other masters are all blaming me.{nl}They told me that I am not doing anything even when those monsters are threatening Klaipeda.{nl}
Do I have to face against those weak monsters?{nl}If you could take care of them, I will teach you the magic of Choronomancer.
It's called an Ironbaum at the west forest of Siaulai.{nl}Even if I am not interested in it, I can't help resist listening since I also have ears.
I wonder what Pyromancer Master would tell by looking at the laid down Ironbaum.{nl}I will teach you the magic of Chronomancer as I promised.
I have a request that I don't want to lose to Linker Master.{nl}If you could take care of that request on behalf of me, I will teach you how to control the energy. How about it?
It is not that hard.{nl}You just have to defeat Beowolf that is walking around this mine village.
I had troubles for that a few times in the past.{nl}But if I have a disciple like you, I won't lose to Linker Master anymore.
That's nice!{nl}Leave the Linker Master and let's talk about the energy in details.
If you want to learn about my magic, there is something that you should do for me.{nl}Defeat the Beowolf that appeared in the mine village quicker than Psychochino Master.
Beowolf is not easy, but you would be able to defeat it.{nl}You applied to become a linker right?
Well done. I wonder what Psychochino Master would feel after looking at the laid down Beowolf.{nl}I will teach you my magic as I promised to you.
Monsters are making a chaos near Fedimian.{nl}As a result, masters are working together to defeat them.{nl}How about it, if you are an applicant to become a Thaumaturge, I think you should also help.
Good. You are qualified as a Thaumaturge.{nl}As I promised, I will enhance you.
I can still picture the faces of the other masters.{nl}Not only that, I am happy to get a good disciple.
It doesn't make sense to stay in the safe place as a master when there are full of monsters.{nl}I thought that's not right so I ran from Fedimian.{nl}
I heard that Necrobenter appeared again at the old garden of the goddess.{nl}If you dream to be a sorcerer, I hope you follow my request.
It is silly to stay in the safe place as a master.{nl}
I understand your point.{nl}I will teach you magic as I promised to you.
I can teach you my magic whenever you want.{nl}But, I am not sure if you could follow well.
If that's the case, please defeat Necrobenter that appears at the old garden of the goddess.{nl}I can teach you my magic when you can do that.
You are more than I expected.{nl}But, the magic to control time is really hard so you should prepare for it.
Long time no see. You want to be an Alchemist.{nl}I should test you if you are worth to be an Alchemist.
Good.{nl}Please defeat the Beowolf that is making mess around here.{nl}
It is not hard to learn the knowledge of Alchemmist.{nl}You can learn the basics such as decomposition of an element, synthesis and etc slowly.
Good. I am looking forward for your future.{nl}I will advance you to Alchemist.

You should prove your determination to remove the vicious power to follow the training of a priest.{nl}Please get the pocket with demonic energy from the bubbes at the first floor of the crystal mine.
Please talk to the elder of the crystal mine if you have hard time entering the crystal mine.
I will purify these pockets so that it won't release the demonic power anymore.{nl}Brother, I welcome you to be a priest.
Brother. You came far to learn the religious belief of Krivi, but I don't have to time to greet you at the moment.
The brother who brought the divine object disappeared.{nl}I beg you for the mercy of the goddess. Can you find our brother?
Krivi siblings
Don't come near!{nl}The monsters that are after the divine objects are coming!
I was so afraid that I would not be able to bring the divine objects to Klaipeda.{nl}Brother, you must be the messenger that the goddess sent.
The last call stopped at the crystal mine.{nl}The brother should be safe.. I am so worried.
I have a lot more to do.{nl}Don't worry and please pass this divine object to Krivi Master.
How can I say this object is more important than a person.{nl}This is all due to the blessing of the goddess that our brother and him are all safe.{nl}
Anyways, we welcome you to be a member of Krivi.{nl}The goddess must be happy to see you.
You should prove yourself that you are suited to a sword if you want to reach a higher level of swordsmanship.{nl}Please obtain the heart of Stone Orca at the first floor of the crystal mine.
There is nothing more important than a life.{nl}If you want to use a sword, you should be determined.
Okay that's it.. you collected well.{nl}I will teach you how to become a person who is suited well for swords.
The magic won't distinguish people, but I don't like a lazy person.{nl}Defeat Shredded at the first floor of the crystal mine.
If you don't train well yourself, I won't accept in the name of the wizard.{nl}Learn hundred times and train thousand times to become a real sword.
I understand your determination.{nl}I will teach you well so that you become the person suitable to be a wizard.
You want to learn my skills?{nl}It's not hard to teach, but, would you be able to master my lesson?
If you can't bring arrows, you better give up quickly.
Okay. You are passeed.{nl}I will teach you well to be a nice archer.
Cleric helps others to reach higher stage.{nl}To cure other people, please get me the green ointment from the bubbes at the first floor of the crystal mine.{nl}{nl}
The goddess told you to help you around.{nl}By helping others near, that will help your spirit as well.
I think I can relieve the pains of many patients with this.{nl}As a cleric master, I will help you to contribute more to the goddess.
Defeat the bats at the first floor of the crystal mine and bring me the wings of them as a proof.
If you could give us the blessing of cure, you can reach near to the goddess even more.{nl}By helping others, I will help you reach to a higher stage of Cleric.
Lots of people come here after receiving attacks from monsters.{nl}But since I ran out of the herbs, we have no choice but to give first aid to the patients.
Thanks.{nl}As a cleric master, I will help you to accomplish a higher mission.
{nl}Maybe I can help you what the real battels feel like before you receive lessons from me.{nl}
You can find Honeypins when you go to the forest.{nl}They will be a good experience for you at the moment.
You should train hard like real battles, but do not forget the word, be careful.
Good. I can see that you are much better now.{nl}If you want to learn, please come often.
Your heroic stories are good lessons for us, Peltastas.{nl}But, I should check myself to accept you as my disciple.
Stories are always exaggerated.{nl}So forgive me that I am acting so picky.
It was not an exaggeration.{nl}Since your skill is proven, I will accept you to learn the lessons of Peltasta.
The only thing you can trust in real battles is your experience.{nl}If you want to learn the swordsmanship of Highlander, it will be good to accumulate good experiences.
There is a monster called Honeypin at the forest.{nl}Facing that monster will be a good experience.
Well done.{nl}You will become a good swordsman if you gain more experiences and learn from me.
To be called a Hoplite, You should act well so everyone can rely you and trust you.{nl}Your skills are already famous here, but I want to check them with my own eyes.
I thought more time would take, you are better than I thought.{nl}I am counting on you as a colleague.
It is strange that a skillful person like you learn from me.{nl}But, there is a cost to any learning.
So I guess it was easily over.{nl}Good. You are qualified.{nl}
You should become strong to show others. Don't you think so?
Good. You skills are enough.{nl}I am happy to teach you,.
There is nothing that will come in my way as I decided to become a Catapract. {nl}Just penetrate into anything that would block against us. Don't you think so?
You are more than I expected.{nl}Good. Let's continue our good relationship.

I am sorry, but, I am too busy myself to accept you since I am so busy personally at the moment.{nl}I heard someone saw the symbol of our family that was lost on the divine day so I am looking after for it.
I am the only one left at Legwyn Family so each symbol is important to me.
For me, the life of a pirate is fighting, stealing, fighting again and stealing again.{nl}My fellows, drink up!
Very reliable.{nl}Good. I will teach you my skills from now on.
This is a very dangerous request that other masters feel uncomfortable with.{nl}If you want more, you should accept more dangerous requests.
I will recognize your skills as I promised to you. {nl}Follow me. I will open the way of Doppelsoeldner to you.
I lost an important divine object of Krivi.{nl}If you want to reach to a higher stage of Krivi, I will help you find the divine object again.
There is a strong power within the divine objects so lots of monsters are going after for them.{nl}Losing a divine object is like losing a faith.
Well done. Fortunately, the divine object is okay.{nl}I will teach you the training of Krivi as I promised to you.
I heard vicious energy is coming from the Ruklys street these days.{nl}If you want to walk the way of a Priest, You should exorcise in the name of the goddess.
The vicious energy is the real evil.{nl}But I am sure you will be able to exorcise the energy in Ruklys street.
This is a important divine object that was trasferring to Klaipeda.{nl}I heard that they were attacked while they were walking on the main street of the petrified citiy.{nl}I am counting on you.
Well done.{nl}I will teach you everything about Bokor as I promised to you.
If I could obtain solid woods from the main street of the petrified city, I can accept any requests..{nl}For example, the lesson of Divdirbys.
That is my lifelong wish.{nl}That tree always gestures towards me to make itself into a masterpiece.
Oh. That's it.{nl}You can come to me anytime when you want to learn the lessons of Divdirbys!
You have done a good job.{nl}I will look forward to your growth as a Sadhu Master.
I heard enough about you that you have a firm religious belief.{nl}But, I want to check it with my own eyes.
Prove your religious belief.{nl}There's nothing to be worried about. The goddess will protect you.
You have done well.{nl}With this, your religious belief is proven so I will accept you to learn my lessons.
Good. I will accept your determination.{nl}I always tell you, but our Monk training is really harsh.
At the moment when I didn't know what to do, the goddess sent you.{nl}Anyways, I congratulate you to become a Pardoner.
Oracle Master
Even when the goddess is absent, oracle should pass the oracle well.{nl}I will test whether you are qualified for it by dueling against you.
I checked your competence well enough.{nl}As an oracle master, I will help you interpret the oracle well.

First, please bring Glizardon's bone from the 1st basement and Galok's hair from the 1st floor of Tenet Cathedral.{nl}And also bring me the fragments of Egnome from the 2nd floor. Okay then I am counting on you.
Reality changes as I wish. And it becomes possible just by thinking!{nl}That's called super natural power.{nl}The amount of the power depends on how one belives in his power..{nl}
Okay, so you want to be a Psychochino?{nl}If you could help my work a bit, I will help you find your hidden abilities.
Please bring me the essences of Minotaurs and Chapparition from Gate Route.{nl}Okay.. I am counting on you.
Okay. This is it. I can tell it's full of demonic power by just looking at its color.{nl}I will teach you what the real Psychochino is from now on so you should get ready!
My old colleague who went to Sirudgellar Forest told me that he saw a strange looking map.{nl}I am sure that it is the map we are looking for.
I heard Minotaurs has it somewhere in the Sirudgellar Forest.{nl}That monster is not easy so you should be prepared a lot.
Ebonippon..{nl}Ranger Master still seems to have some regret.{nl}
I was Elementalist Master talking to a man wearing a hood.{nl}I can't say for sure if that's him, but I can never forget the fragrance.
After talking to Elementalist, he disappeared into darkness.{nl}You better go and talk to him.
I told him that it would be obtainable in Sirudgellar Forest.{nl}That's the place where even the famous Rodelero Master's search team ran away from.
I am looking for a trace of a man. His name is Ebonippon.{nl}I heard Sadhu Master at Akmens Ridge has his information so go there.
It's not a huge task. I want you to help my experiment..{nl}First, please bring me burnable juice of Tonturia from Zachariel Intersection.
In fact, Tonturia is nothing, but the fact that there are lots of other monsters nearby is more dangerous.{nl}Hmm.. Good Luck!
My father is a merchant who comes to Fedimian often.{nl}But after he went into Sirudgellar Forest do some transaction, he never returned.{nl}
I heard a solider at Fedimian saw a luggage of a merchat in Sirudgellar Forest.{nl}The only one I can trust right now is you. Please.. I am counting on you!
This is the symbol that I engraved on my father's sleeve..{nl}This is so precious to me... Thank you.
Please bring me Hogma Spellers and Canines of Guards at Plateau of Rex.{nl}It won't be hard to you.{nl}
I like your determination.{nl}Please defeat Sparnas Man at Vieta Valley to prove your skills.
Cathapract is a warrior who stands in front of anyone and fight.{nl}If there are barriers in the way, just penetrate into them.{nl}I came with a good idea.
Contratulations for passing the test.{nl}My lessons are strict so I hope you follow well.
Sparnas Man at Vieta Valley is said to be threatening people.{nl}He will not be an easy opponent, but he will be enough to prove your skills.
The most important attribute Peltasta thinks is courage.{nl}Since Peltasta shouldn't avoid enemies' attacks and block them with their shields.
Before you learn lessons from me, you should show me how brave you are.{nl}
Don't worry since I will adjust the level of dueling to your level.{nl}Okay then I will begin!
I will show you any weapon such as a bow or a gun. Come on.
As I was transferring the research materials that I discovered before, a few of them flew away due to wind.{nl}They are at Ramstis Canyon, but I don't have time to find them. I am counting on you.
You found them sooner than I expected.{nl}Good. I will help you pull out your abilities as a Thaumaturge.
Please get me Hogma Spellers, Blood of Hogma Guards,{nl}and lastly, Blood of Hogma Commander from Zachariel Intersection.
Sparnas Man at Vieta Valley would fit your reputation..{nl}Show him what's the true power of serving the goddess like.
How many time did this happen already?{nl}I am sorry, but, please go meet Flecther Master to find out what happened.{nl}Go to Esanchiu Village.
That dumb assistant captain took all of them and ran away to Poslinkis Forest.{nl}Maybe monsters may have them. I hope so.
There are fishing rods which Red Fishermen are carrying at Saknis Fields.{nl}When you knock on them, a clear sound will come out. Please bring me those.
Although you learned lessons from me, I don't know if you could use all of them.{nl}I will give you an assignment. Hunt for various monsters.
Bushspiders from Katyn Forest Entrance, Ellomagos from Owls' cemetry, and green Pokubons from Poslinkis Forest.{nl}Of course, I will give you some baits.
If you dream of reaching a higher stage as a Mugosa, there's an assignment I will give to you.{nl}Collect special poisions from Bites at Saknis Fields.
There are needles with the ointment on them that I crafted in this pot.{nl}When you hit Bites with these, you would be able to collect poisons.
It is your assignment to hunt for hidden monsters.{nl}The location is Saknis Fields. {nl}If you want to be a Scout, you should do it. Dont you think so?
You want to learn from me. {nl}
If that's the case, I want you to make a bet with Hackapell Master on behalf of me.{nl}He thinks there is a thing in the world that can't be penetrated.{nl}
If he asks you, I will tell that our competent Hopelite defeated it.{nl}I will now acknowlege your skills.
I heard that the other masters sent the disciples to defeat Yekubs at Owls' Cemetry.{nl}But that's the task you should complete. Go there.
Leadeaship needs to be supported by the faith from the colleagues and the accumulated experiences.{nl}I will first have to find out if you are competent enough to command other people.
When you go to the garden of Green Family, you can meet Collimencia.{nl}You are worth to be a Centurion if you could defeat it.
This is the rope to tie up people.{nl}Practice with it enough at Poslinkis Forest so you would be able to manage it well.{nl}Let's talk about my lesson after that.
Bitereginas are threatening people at Owls' Village.{nl}What do you think? I want you defeat them as a compensation for my lessons.
With the name of Master, I should help others around, but I just don't have time.{nl}Anyways, I will teach you my skills as I promised to you.
If you tell me like that, I can tell you there is a solution.{nl}If you could defeat Moas at the outer edge of Fedimian who destroyed all my ingredients, I will change your turn.
I heard Hackapell Master would defeat Shadow Gailers at Owls' Village..{nl}It will be good to see if you could defeat them first.
A skilled person like you would defeat Reaverpedes at Roxona Market easily.{nl}If you can't do this, I can't accept you as a Ranger applicant.
Some idiot baron opened a portal that was connected to Demons' Prison.{nl}I heard that the demons there are keep trying to come out.{nl}
Defeat Deadbone which is the most dangerous demon there.{nl}Don't you think it will be a good hunt?
You want to learn my skills?{nl}If you could bring me burnable woods from Jonna Jolems at Aqueduct, I will think about it.
Do you know this?{nl}I heard that Rajatoad at the 1st zone of Demons' Prison possess dangerous poison.{nl}
We increase our level of immunity by controlling many different types of poisons.{nl}If you could survive from that poison, I will teach you how to control poison well.
You want to be a Schwarze?{nl}It is very easy to learn how to control guns.{nl}
But, it becomes a totally different story if you want to keep aiming the enemy rushing in.{nl}I mean courage. Why don't we check it out?{nl}
Demons' prison, I heard some dumb landlord opened the portal to the place where there are full of monsters.{nl}Hunt for Deadbone there. It will be very fun.
Very nice. I feel like I am seeing myself in the past.{nl}Since you are Schwarze now, we can be mirrors to each other from now.
I heard that Minotaurs has shown up at Roxona Market.{nl}Please bring me the proof of its death.
It seems like the number of demons is keep increasing.{nl}I heard other masters are also having some troubles.
The number of Blue Puragis at Saknis Fields has increased a lot recently and threatening villagers there.{nl}If you want to reach a higher level as a true Sahdu, show your abilities there.
Mothstem? I saw it from the outer edge of Fedimian. {nl}Pardoner Master was also looking for it. I guess he hasn't found it yet.
Instead of introducing yourself in words, it will be way better to show your abilities.{nl}My assignment is to defeat Reaverpedes at Esanchiu village.
Reaverpedes at Esanchiu village would fit your reputation.{nl}I heard your name enough already, but I should see myself.
What present?{nl}What do you think will be the most precious gift for Necromancer?
If you want to learn my magics, I should first know how competent you are.{nl}Reaverpedes at Esanchiu village would fit your reputation.
Oh, such a great courage.{nl}If you could defeat Nederbovines from Poslinkis Forest, I will advance you.
All the masters around here are chasing after the monsters.{nl}You should defeat that monsters quicker than anybody to learn my magics.
It is called Nederbovine.{nl}According to a reliable source, it recently appeared at Poslinkis Forest.
There are more wounded people, but the amount of herbs we have is lacking.{nl}Please collect Wildflower Alcohol from Roxona Market for them.
There's a monster called Collimencia at Grinas Hill Areas.{nl}It is a threatening monster, but you should defeat it easily.
Poatas at Grinas Hill Areas if well known for attacking people.{nl}If you could defeat them, they will be enough.
If you want to learn from me, you should first show your skills to me.{nl}Collimencias at the garden of Green Family would fit your reputation.
If you want to be a Cathapract, then you should be able to defeat Gaigalas at Tenents Farm.{nl}If you understand, hurry up.
This.. It must be the symbol of Regwyn Family.{nl}Thank you. As I promised, I will help you to reach to a higher level.
You must first show your abilities before you start to learn from me. That's the manner.{nl}I think Honeypins at Tenents' Farm would be enough.
I will be able to check your skills if you could defeat Gaigalas at Grinas Training Field.{nl}Good luck.
Okay then.. I think I can test your skills with this.{nl}I heard there's a person who saw Poata at the garden of Green Family swallowing the symbol.{nl}Okay then, I am counting on you.
I am sorry, but the way of Bokor can't be searched by anyone.{nl}If you could bring me the essence of petrified whale at Roxona Makert, I will acknowledge your skills.
Petrified Whales at Roxona maket killed many people.{nl}I need the essence with the hatred from the people who were killed.
It is important for Sadhu to understand others' pains.{nl}Understanding their minds will be the source to increase the power of Sadhu.{nl}
Please forgive me for being too picky since this task is being done in the name of Paladin.{nl}Gaigalas at Tenents' Farm would fit your name.

If you want to reach higher level of Monk, please show me the determination that you would endure strict training.{nl}After defeating Nederbovine at Poslinkis Forest and bring me the proof, I will acknowledge your skills.
Our training is very strict.{nl}You would be able to follow our training if you could defeat Nederbovines at Poslinkis Forest.
There's a something that you should do instead of an entrance test to become a Pardoner.{nl}Retrieve the money of the lost indulgence at the region near Aqueduct. You can do it right?
